name: Queen of SWORDS
description:
I've created this piece with a photo, for me it's like a self-portrait. This photo is from 2020, I was recovering from a really bad accident, couldn't walk for several months. The sword is real and I've found it in the streets, almost in front of my own home.

This drawning style is the same I develop since 2015/16 in my murals/paintings.
